{"tid":2488692,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"張馨月自爆與林峯拍拖初期曾遭反對 靠食口水尾打動外母","createTime":"2021-04-14T11:43:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T14:35:36.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"cb6ab098cb45c2143b5161a8f726c95a54e62215","tid":2488692,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T11:43:18.000Z","msg":"不過一講到和藝人拍拖有壓力，林峯指還好啦，張馨月反而說：「開始時我父母都不同意，但有次他帶早餐來我家時，我媽當日胃不太舒服，吃了幾啖就沒吃了，結果剩餘的他竟然吃了，我媽看到覺得他太真誠，吃過的他都不嫌棄，然後又餵我媽食飯，就這樣把我媽的心立刻融化。」林峯這個舉動令張媽媽感覺有個兒子一樣，成功獲得歡心，現場主持人聽到都十分譁然。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210414/27Y7DCADVJHNFJQKEQZDVVMN5U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210414%2F27Y7DCADVJHNFJQKEQZDVVMN5U%2F&d=t2%2FAN0mLur8%2Bj%2B1TvbkzvudFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=96b3937d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210414%2F27Y7DCADVJHNFJQKEQZDVVMN5U%2F&h=93242ce4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210414/27Y7DCADVJHNFJQKEQZDVVMN5U/</a>"},{"pid":"a3fdd936f008dd92e5ecdabf00c90b27e6732258","tid":2488692,"uid":84081,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T11:45:18.000Z","msg":"係咪大陸冇GOOGLE, 唔知林峰幾多身家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35d2b8296b569689d262b85c10e8b7ed67815aa8","tid":2488692,"uid":8410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T11:45:27.000Z","msg":"吳千語呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85a045650ea7ed5b957db99a8c99dfab3a9092f4","tid":2488692,"uid":91833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T11:46:16.000Z","msg":"醉翁之意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99589336947c9c854ed51c1e12d50dcbb3e37b55","tid":2488692,"uid":23445,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T11:48:45.000Z","msg":"唔知峯仔有冇食埋佢老